{"tid":1967983,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港共︰疫情回落 港共有功","createTime":"2020-04-11T10:26:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-11T11:12:33.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"dddaf64599222d35793551ff04f2895b1da1d922","tid":1967983,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T10:26:25.000Z","msg":"曾浩輝︰確診個案數目仍偏多 市民仍要繼續忍耐<br />\n11.04.2020 18:04<br />\n<br />\n政府的社交平台專頁「添馬台」，刊登衛生防護中心前總監曾浩輝就本港新型冠狀病毒疫情的分析，指確診個案達到1000宗，近日個案宗數似乎回落，疫情的有效傳播數逐漸下降，顯示防疫措施開始見效，但他指現時個案數目仍然偏多，並可以在短時間內暴增。<br />\n<br />\n曾浩輝認為，社會能否一步步恢復日常生活，視乎環球及內地的疫情、本港醫療系統能否守得住、能否盡快找到感染者與接觸者作診斷及隔離檢疫，以及市民是否可以繼續忍耐，保持社交距離，做好個人衛生。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1280160&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1280160%26csid%3D261_341&d=PwmYTnxQQ9jzt6ozq479VWzUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=a2886ab2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1280160&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"31bfd450af027b762336bf81eaf999defe8e5c9d","tid":1967983,"uid":349872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T10:27:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bb931f613d1adcb6fc49e6eff7f80452516e07f","tid":1967983,"uid":5737,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T10:42:39.000Z","msg":"Lm<br />\n次撚次回落少少就 扮撚哂野<br />\n<br />\n之後就社區大爆發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"880ee09f1370430004b19b89a233e174d93e8c38","tid":1967983,"uid":5737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5bb931f613d1adcb6fc49e6eff7f80452516e07f","tid":1967983,"uid":5737,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T10:42:39.000Z","msg":"Lm<br />\n次撚次回落少少就 扮撚哂野<br />\n<br />\n之後就社區大爆發<img src=\"/assets